new resource page: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Missions: Side Quests for $MIND Token Upside | ScopeLock Resources</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .meta {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .highlight {
            background: #f0f7ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .steps {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .step {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step-number {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .mission-card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .mission-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .mission-reward {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .mission-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        .comparison {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .comparison-box {
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .comparison-box.old {
            background: #fff0f0;
            border: 2px solid #ff4444;
        }
        .comparison-box.new {
            background: #f0fff0;
            border: 2px solid #44ff44;
        }
        .comparison-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .comparison-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .comparison-box li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .timeline {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .timeline-arrow {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .timeline-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .timeline-detail {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffcc00;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #e6f7ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .key-takeaway {
            display: flex;
            align-items: start;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .key-icon {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .key-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .key-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .key-description {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        .cta-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-title {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            .comparison {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .timeline {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .timeline-arrow {
                transform: rotate(90deg);
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="meta">
            ‚Üê Resources
        </div>

        <h1>üéÆ Missions: Side Quests for $MIND Token Upside</h1>

        <div class="meta">
            Nov 21, 2025 ‚Ä¢ 10 min read ‚Ä¢ Team Onboarding Series #4
        </div>

        <div class="highlight">
            "Missions are optional bonus work. Complete them to earn $MIND tokens. If the protocol gains traction, early contributors benefit from token upside."
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Your main income comes from <strong>Jobs</strong> (Upwork client work ‚Üí 30% team pool in dollars). Missions are completely separate: optional side quests that earn you $MIND tokens (launching at $1.00 per token).</p>

            <p>Think of it like this: Jobs pay your rent. Missions build potential equity. Focus on jobs first, grab missions when you have time.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>What Are Missions?</h2>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Missions are specific tasks that help ScopeLock grow. They're not client work‚Äîthey're business development, recruiting, content creation, and community building. Each mission has a fixed $MIND reward.</p>

            <div class="mission-card">
                <div class="mission-title">üìù Write Upwork Proposal</div>
                <div class="mission-reward">1 $MIND</div>
                <div class="mission-description">Draft and submit a proposal for an Upwork job posting. Submit proof (screenshot of sent proposal).</div>
            </div>

            <div class="mission-card">
                <div class="mission-title">üë• Recruit New Team Member</div>
                <div class="mission-reward">10 $MIND</div>
                <div class="mission-description">Bring someone onto the team who completes their first paid job. Submit proof (new member's username).</div>
            </div>

            <div class="mission-card">
                <div class="mission-title">üê¶ Post About ScopeLock on X</div>
                <div class="mission-reward">2 $MIND</div>
                <div class="mission-description">Create and publish a post about ScopeLock on X (Twitter). Submit proof (link to post).</div>
            </div>

            <div class="mission-card">
                <div class="mission-title">üéØ Find a Prospect in Your Telegram Contacts</div>
                <div class="mission-reward">1 $MIND</div>
                <div class="mission-description">Browse your Telegram contacts and identify someone who could use ScopeLock's services. Share our value prop with them. Submit proof (screenshot of outreach).</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How It Works</h2>

        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <strong>Browse available missions</strong><br>
                Go to <a href="https://scopelock.mindprotocol.ai/mission-deck/" target="_blank">scopelock.mindprotocol.ai/mission-deck</a> and see what's available.
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <strong>Claim a mission</strong><br>
                Click "Claim Mission" on one you want to do. You'll have 7 days to complete it. First time? You'll connect your wallet here.
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <strong>Complete the work</strong><br>
                Do the actual task (write proposal, recruit someone, post content, etc.). Work offline if needed.
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <strong>Submit proof</strong><br>
                Upload screenshot, link, or whatever proof the mission requires. System verifies and allocates tokens.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>First-time wallet setup:</strong> When you claim your first mission, you'll be prompted to connect a Solana wallet (we recommend Phantom or MetaMask). This is where your Mind tokens get sent. Takes 60 seconds.
        </div>

        <h2>Jobs vs. Missions: What's The Difference?</h2>

        <div class="comparison">
            <div class="comparison-box new">
                <div class="comparison-title">üí∞ JOBS (Main Income)</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Upwork client work</li>
                    <li>Paid in <strong>dollars (SOL/USDC)</strong></li>
                    <li>30% team pool split by contribution</li>
                    <li>This pays your rent</li>
                    <li><strong>Priority: Focus here first</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="comparison-box old">
                <div class="comparison-title">üéÆ MISSIONS (Token Upside)</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Side quests (proposals, recruiting, posts)</li>
                    <li>Paid in <strong>$MIND tokens</strong></li>
                    <li>Fixed token amount per mission</li>
                    <li>This builds potential equity</li>
                    <li><strong>Optional: Do when you have time</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p><strong>Why separate?</strong> We want you focused on earning real income from jobs. Missions are pure upside‚Äî$MIND launches at $1.00, giving immediate tangible value to your side quest contributions. But you should never sacrifice paid work for missions.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Token Allocation Timeline</h2>

        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-label">Day 0</div>
                <div class="timeline-detail">Claim mission</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-label">Day 1-7</div>
                <div class="timeline-detail">Complete task</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-label">Day 7</div>
                <div class="timeline-detail">Submit proof</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-label">Day 7-9</div>
                <div class="timeline-detail">Verification</div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-label">Day 10</div>
                <div class="timeline-detail">Tokens allocated</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>Token allocation:</strong> $MIND tokens get sent to your connected wallet within ~48 hours of proof verification. You'll see them in your Phantom/MetaMask wallet. Hold them, trade them (after launch), or convert to stablecoins.
        </div>

        <h2>Understanding $MIND Token Upside</h2>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Mind Protocol is building agentic AI infrastructure. ScopeLock is one of the first applications using it. The $MIND token powers the protocol‚Äîthink of it like ETH for Ethereum or SOL for Solana.</p>

            <h3>What gives $MIND tokens value?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Protocol usage:</strong> Every AI interaction in ScopeLock (and other apps) uses $MIND tokens</li>
                <li><strong>Early contributor rewards:</strong> People who help build the ecosystem get airdropped tokens</li>
                <li><strong>Network effects:</strong> More apps using Mind Protocol = more token demand</li>
                <li><strong>Scarcity:</strong> Fixed supply, distributed to contributors over time</li>
                <li><strong>Launch price:</strong> $MIND launches at $1.00, providing clear baseline valuation</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Real-world comparison:</h3>
            <p>Early contributors to protocols like Uniswap, ENS, and dYdX received airdrops worth $5K-50K+ for early participation. Mind Protocol follows similar mechanics: contribute early, earn $MIND, benefit if protocol succeeds.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>Important:</strong> Token value beyond launch is speculative. $MIND launches at $1.00, but market price may rise or fall based on protocol adoption. Treat missions as <strong>optional upside</strong>, not guaranteed income. Your main income is from jobs.
        </div>

        <h2>Mission Completion Tips</h2>

        <div class="section">
            <h3>For Proposal Writing (1 $MIND)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse Upwork for relevant jobs ScopeLock could win</li>
                <li>Write tailored proposal (not copy-paste template)</li>
                <li>Screenshot submission confirmation as proof</li>
                <li>Can batch: claim mission, write 3-5 proposals in one session</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>For Recruiting (10 $MIND)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Share ScopeLock opportunity with developers you know</li>
                <li>They need to join team AND complete first paid job</li>
                <li>Higher barrier = higher reward (10 $MIND)</li>
                <li>Quality over quantity: recruit people who'll actually contribute</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>For Social Posts (2 $MIND)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Share authentic experience working with AI citizens</li>
                <li>Post link to your tweet/X post as proof</li>
                <li>Quick mission: takes 5 minutes, earns $MIND</li>
                <li>Good for when you have 10 minutes between jobs</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>For Finding Prospects (1 $MIND)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Browse your Telegram contacts for agency owners, startup founders, tech leads</li>
                <li>Look for people who've mentioned needing dev work or struggling with delivery</li>
                <li>Share brief message: "Hey, working with this AI-powered agency that delivers in 90s. Thought of you."</li>
                <li>Screenshot your outreach message as proof</li>
                <li>Even if they don't respond immediately, you've planted the seed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div class="section">
            <h3>Can I do missions without doing jobs?</h3>
            <p>Technically yes, but missions alone won't pay rent. Focus on jobs (30% team pool in dollars) for income. Missions are bonus.</p>

            <h3>What if I claim a mission but don't complete it?</h3>
            <p>After 7 days, mission becomes available again for others to claim. No penalty, but don't claim if you're not going to complete‚Äîit blocks others.</p>

            <h3>Can I complete the same mission multiple times?</h3>
            <p>Depends on mission type. "Write Upwork Proposal" = yes, can claim again after completing. "Recruit Team Member" = once per person recruited.</p>

            <h3>When can I sell $MIND tokens?</h3>
            <p>$MIND launches at $1.00 on supported DEXs. After launch, you can hold, trade, or convert to stablecoins. Early contributors who accumulate pre-launch tokens benefit from immediate liquidity.</p>

            <h3>Do missions expire?</h3>
            <p>No. As long as ScopeLock operates, missions will be available. The token allocation per mission might change over time (early = more generous), but missions don't expire.</p>

            <h3>What if proof verification fails?</h3>
            <p>You'll get notification explaining why (e.g., screenshot unclear, proposal not actually sent). Fix and resubmit. Fair verification process.</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="key-takeaway">
                <div class="key-icon">üí∞</div>
                <div class="key-content">
                    <div class="key-title">Jobs = Income, Missions = Upside</div>
                    <div class="key-description">Focus on paid jobs first. Missions are optional bonus for token accumulation.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="key-takeaway">
                <div class="key-icon">üéØ</div>
                <div class="key-content">
                    <div class="key-title">Clear value from launch</div>
                    <div class="key-description">$MIND launches at $1.00. Complete 10 proposals = 10 $MIND. Recruit 2 people = 20 $MIND. Value is immediate, not speculative.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="key-takeaway">
                <div class="key-icon">‚ö°</div>
                <div class="key-content">
                    <div class="key-title">Simple process: Claim ‚Üí Complete ‚Üí Submit</div>
                    <div class="key-description">Takes 60 seconds to claim, 5-30 minutes to complete (depending on mission), tokens allocated within 48 hours.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="key-takeaway">
                <div class="key-icon">üåç</div>
                <div class="key-content">
                    <div class="key-title">No geographic disadvantage</div>
                    <div class="key-description">Missions pay same tokens regardless of location. Token upside is global, not PPP-adjusted.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="key-takeaway">
                <div class="key-icon">üìà</div>
                <div class="key-content">
                    <div class="key-title">Risk-reward is clear</div>
                    <div class="key-description">Time investment = 5-30 min per mission. Baseline value = 1-10 $MIND at launch. Upside = potential token appreciation if protocol succeeds.</div>
                </div>
            </d>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-box">
            <div class="cta-title">Ready to Start Earning Tokens?</div>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Browse available missions and claim your first one. Wallet setup takes 60 seconds.</p>
            <a href="https://scopelock.mindprotocol.ai/mission-deck/" class="cta-button" target="_blank">Open Mission Deck ‚Üí</a>
        </div>

        <div class="section" style="margin-top: 60px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 2px solid #eee;">
            <h3>Related Resources</h3>
            <ul style="font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 2;">
                <li><strong>üí∞ The More You Work, The More You Earn</strong> - Understand main compensation from jobs</li>
                <li><strong>üîÑ The Complete Mission Flow</strong> - Understand who does what when</li>
                <li><strong>üí¨ How to Talk to AI Citizens</strong> - Get better output from Rafael and Sofia</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section" style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px;">
            <h3>Questions About Missions?</h3>
            <p>Reach out to Nicolas on Telegram (<a href="https://t.me/nlr_ai" target="_blank">@nlr_ai</a>) or ask in the team chat. We're building this system together‚Äîyour feedback helps improve it for everyone.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> --- Of course, style it in a coherent way with the other resource pages. You can improve it a bit if you want. And let's go!
